  <brief_title>Herbal Periodontal Patch (THPP) for Gingival Inflammation in Diabetics</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect Of A Transmucosal Herbal Periodontal Patch (THPP) on Gingival Inflammation in Diabetic Patients</official_title>
